name: The 7 secrets of Beppe - secret 4 of 7
description:
The 7 secrets of Beppe

The 7 Secrets Of Beppe is an artwork made of 7 password encrypted compressed archive files containing each one a different secret to unveil and a gif file as thropy and proof of decryption. 

Each one of the 7 secrets of Beppe will be revealed to humanity when there will be enough available computational power and will to be worth to brute force it or when the Predestined One will succeed to guess the password. 

The seventh and last secret will be the reward Beppe will gift to the first mortal who will be able to collect and decrypts the other 6 secrets.
